Remember only if it proves very distressed several times, it is advisable to consult a doctor or check what causes so much anxiety in the child.
If you understand what it says (which is not normal), do not have the temptation to question him for information.
You will get nothing, because while sleeping, he is not aware to be able to organize his thoughts.
In addition, you will hear what he says, but you won't know what it is dreaming, be careful suddenly to the way in which you interpreting the information and the conclusions that you draw.
Never tell the child that you can question him during the night to know its secrets.
